# Plaintext runtime/secret files are never committed. Real secrets live here as
# sops-encrypted `enc.env` (and *.enc) blobs — safe to commit — and are
# decrypted to a gitignored `.env` on the host by Komodo's pre_deploy step.
*.env
!enc.env
*.enc.tmp
*-fetch.json
config/
!stacks/actual/cli/config/
!stacks/actual/cli/config/*.json
data/
matter-server/
ledfx-config/
cache/
ledfx.log*
